 decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" src="/images/quotation-mark.svg"/></div><div class="testimonial-card_testimonialContent__IwvIl"><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_testimonialText__5AZJY">My name is Amit Patel and I’m a resident of Jaipur, Rajasthan and I’d like to share our great experience with Fino Payment bank.I am grateful to know my family’s life savings that are invested in this company are protected by a simple but effective safeguard with this bank. Definitely happy we chose Fino Payment Bank!!! </p><div class="testimonial-card_providerInfo__rW2ms"><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_providerName__A1ewr">Amit Patel</p><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_providerDesignation__pAQkS"></p><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_providerLocation__jklTE"></p></div></div></div></div></div><div role="group" aria-roledescription="slide" aria-label="1 of 4" aria-hidden="false" class="flex-shrink-0 transition-all duration-300 z-10" style="width:33%" data-active="true"><div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full relative h-full carousel-item-wrapper-active carousel-item-active" data-carousel-active="true"><div class="testimonial-card_testimonialCard__nWlSz testimonial-card_carouselItemActive__4JwRM carousel-item-active"><div class="testimonial-card_testimonialCardIcon__daZau"><img alt="Quotation Mark" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" src="/images/quotation-mark.svg"/></div><div class="testimonial-card_testimonialContent__IwvIl"><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_testimonialText__5AZJY">My name is Nikhil Patel and I’m a resident of Ahmedabad, Gujarat and I took a ‘Family floater’ Insurance cover through Fino in the year 2018. During my family emergency, this policy was of great assistance to my mom’s treatment. My fund disbursal was super smooth and hassle-free. </p><div class="testimonial-card_providerInfo__rW2ms"><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_providerName__A1ewr">Nikhil Patel</p><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_providerDesignation__pAQkS"></p><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_providerLocation__jklTE"></p></div></div></div></div></div><div role="group" aria-roledescription="slide" aria-label="2 of 4" aria-hidden="true" class="flex-shrink-0 transition-all duration-300 z-0" style="width:33%" data-active="false"><div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full relative h-full" data-carousel-active="false"><div class="testimonial-card_testimonialCard__nWlSz"><div class="testimonial-card_testimonialCardIcon__daZau"><img alt="Quotation Mark" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" src="/images/quotation-mark.svg"/></div><div class="testimonial-card_testimonialContent__IwvIl"><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_testimonialText__5AZJY">I am delighted to share my positive experience with Fino Payments Bank in Bastar, Chhattisgarh. Living in a smaller town, accessibility to banking services can sometimes be a challenge. However, I was pleasantly surprised by the bank&#x27;s commitment to customer convenience. What stood out the most for me was the availability of bank Merchants even on Sundays. </p><div class="testimonial-card_providerInfo__rW2ms"><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_providerName__A1ewr">Rohit Yadav</p><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_providerDesignation__pAQkS"></p><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_providerLocation__jklTE"></p></div></div></div></div></div><div role="group" aria-roledescription="slide" aria-label="3 of 4" aria-hidden="true" class="flex-shrink-0 transition-all duration-300 z-0" style="width:33%" data-active="false"><div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full relative h-full" data-carousel-active="false"><div class="testimonial-card_testimonialCard__nWlSz"><div class="testimonial-card_testimonialCardIcon__daZau"><img alt="Quotation Mark" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" src="/images/quotation-mark.svg"/></div><div class="testimonial-card_testimonialContent__IwvIl"><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_testimonialText__5AZJY">My name is Ashish Behera and I stay in Chaibasa, Jharkhand. I wish to share my positive experience with Fino Payments Bank. My younger brother stays away from the family for education and therefore, Fino is a reliable to send/receive money anytime anyday. </p><div class="testimonial-card_providerInfo__rW2ms"><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_providerName__A1ewr">Ashish Behra</p><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_providerDesignation__pAQkS"></p><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_providerLocation__jklTE"></p></div></div></div></div></div><div role="group" aria-roledescription="slide" aria-label="4 of 4" aria-hidden="true" class="flex-shrink-0 transition-all duration-300 z-0" style="width:33%" data-active="false"><div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full relative h-full" data-carousel-active="false"><div class="testimonial-card_testimonialCard__nWlSz"><div class="testimonial-card_testimonialCardIcon__daZau"><img alt="Quotation Mark" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" src="/images/quotation-mark.svg"/></div><div class="testimonial-card_testimonialContent__IwvIl"><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_testimonialText__5AZJY">My name is Amit Patel and I’m a resident of Jaipur, Rajasthan and I’d like to share our great experience with Fino Payment bank.I am grateful to know my family’s life savings that are invested in this company are protected by a simple but effective safeguard with this bank. Definitely happy we chose Fino Payment Bank!!! </p><div class="testimonial-card_providerInfo__rW2ms"><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_providerName__A1ewr">Amit Patel</p><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_providerDesignation__pAQkS"></p><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_providerLocation__jklTE"></p></div></div></div></div></div><div role="group" aria-roledescription="slide" aria-label="1 of 4" aria-hidden="true" class="flex-shrink-0 transition-all duration-300 z-0" style="width:33%" data-active="false"><div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full relative h-full" data-carousel-active="false"><div class="testimonial-card_testimonialCard__nWlSz"><div class="testimonial-card_testimonialCardIcon__daZau"><img alt="Quotation Mark" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" src="/images/quotation-mark.svg"/></div><div class="testimonial-card_testimonialContent__IwvIl"><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_testimonialText__5AZJY">My name is Nikhil Patel and I’m a resident of Ahmedabad, Gujarat and I took a ‘Family floater’ Insurance cover through Fino in the year 2018. During my family emergency, this policy was of great assistance to my mom’s treatment. My fund disbursal was super smooth and hassle-free. </p><div class="testimonial-card_providerInfo__rW2ms"><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_providerName__A1ewr">Nikhil Patel</p><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_providerDesignation__pAQkS"></p><p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-900 text-left testimonial-card_providerLocation__jklTE"></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-3 mt-4 pb-2 navigation-controls"><button type="button" class="p-1 cursor-pointer text-[var(--color-1)] hover:text-[var(--color-1-hover)] transition-opacity focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-400 focus:ring-offset-2 rounded-full disabled:opacity-50" aria-label="Previous slide"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 320 512" height="20" width="20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M41.4 233.4c-12.5 12.5-12.5 32.8 0 45.3l160 160c12.5 12.5 32.8 12.5 45.3 0s12.5-32.8 0-45.3L109.3 256 246.6 118.6c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3s-32.8-12.5-45.3 0l-160 160z"></path></svg></button><div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-2" role="group" aria-label="Slide navigation"><button type="button" aria-label="Go to slide 1 of 4 (current)" aria-current="true" class="dot-controls h-2 bg-[var(--color-1)] focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-400 focus:ring-offset-2 cursor-pointer hover:border-gray-500 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 disabled:opacity-50 w-8"></button><button type="button" aria-label="Go to slide 2 of 4" class="dot-controls w-2 h-2 bg-[var(--color-1)] focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-400 focus:ring-offset-2 cursor-pointer hover:border-gray-500 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 disabled:opacity-50"></button><button type="button" aria-label="Go to slide 3 of 4" class="dot-controls w-2 h-2 bg-[var(--color-1)] focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-400 focus:ring-offset-2 cursor-pointer hover:border-gray-500 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 disabled:opacity-50"></button><button type="button" aria-label="Go to slide 4 of 4" class="dot-controls w-2 h-2 bg-[var(--color-1)] focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-400 focus:ring-offset-2 cursor-pointer hover:border-gray-500 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 disabled:opacity-50"></button></div><button type="button" class="p-1 cursor-pointer text-[var(--color-1)] hover:text-[var(--color-1-hover)] transition-opacity focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-400 focus:ring-offset-2 rounded-full disabled:opacity-50" aria-label="Next slide"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 320 512" height="20" width="20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><path d="M285.476 272.971L91.132 467.314c-9.373 9.373-24.569 9.373-33.941 0l-22.667-22.667c-9.357-9.357-9.375-24.522-.04-33.901L188.505 256 34.484 101.255c-9.335-9.379-9.317-24.544.04-33.901l22.667-22.667c9.373-9.373 24.569-9.373 33.941 0L285.475 239.03c9.373 9.372 9.373 24.568.001 33.941z"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></section><section class="container-margin faq-section pl-container faqSection_faqSection___lA5h" aria-labelledby="_R_2f9m_"><div class="faqSection_contentSection__kuxUs"><h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-left sec-heading small-sec-heading faqSection_sectionHeading__KZo1U" id="_R_2f9m_">FAQ&#x27;s</h2><div class="faq-list_faqList__kz5wT faqSection_faqListSectionContainer__c5AK6"><ol id="_R_mf9m_" class="faq-list_faqList__kz5wT" aria-label="Frequently Asked Questions"><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-0" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-0"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">What is a FinoPay Savings Account?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-0" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-0" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p><span>FinoPay Digital Savings Account brings you great benefits and features to help you save and grow your money. The account comes with a free Personalised Platinum RuPay Debit card and no commitment to maintain any minimum monthly average balance, all at a nominal annual subscription fees.</span></p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-1" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-1"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">Who is eligible to open a FinoPay Savings Account?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-1" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-1" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p><span>FinoPay Savings Account can be opened only by an individual resident of India and age between 18 to 55 years.</span></p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-2" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-2"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">How can I open a FinoPay Savings Account?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-2" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-2" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p><span>You can open FinoPay Savings Account through the option available in the FinoPay App or our website, links are given below:</span><br><span>To download the app:&nbsp;</span><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.finopaymentbank.mobile" target="_blank" rel="noopener">fino payment bank</a><span></span><br><span>Through website:&nbsp;</span><a href="https://digisa.fino.bank.in/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">fino bank</a></p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-3" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-3"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">What documents do I need to open a FinoPay Savings Account?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-3" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-3" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p>To open an account you need the following documents:<br>- Aadhar Card<br>- PAN Card<br>- Mobile number linked with Aadhar.</p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-4" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-4"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">What does the Zero Balance feature mean?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-4" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-4" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p>Zero balance means, no need to keep any minimum balance in the account and no extra charges for balance maintenance.</p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-5" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-5"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">Are there any charges for operating FinoPay Savings Account?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-5" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-5" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p><a href="https://www.fino.bank.in/files/fino/media/post_attachments/sites/default/files/2025-10/English%20%26%20hindi_Saving%20account_Schedule%20of%20Charges_25%20Sep-2025%20%28WebSite%29%20All.pdf" target="_blank" rel="dofollow noopener">Click here</a><span>&nbsp;</span>to view the Schedule of Charges associated to a FinoPay Savings Account.</p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-6" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-6"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">What are the different ways I can add money/transfer funds to my account?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-6" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-6" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p>You can add funds to your Savings Account by one of the following ways:<br>- Via any other bank&rsquo;s NetBanking/Mobile app. Simply add your FinoPay account details<br>&ndash; Account number and IFSC code<br>- Depositing a cheque/cash at any of our branches or merchant point<br>- Using any UPI app using your UPI ID</p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi faq-list_faqItemLastVisible__vrTqj"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-7" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-7"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">What are the modes through which I can access and keep a track on transactions in my FinoPay Savings Account?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-7" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-7" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p>We offer multiple methods to track your FinoPay Savings Account. Here are a few ways you can do it:<br>- Mobile App (To download, click on the link<span>&nbsp;</span><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.finopaymentbank.mobile" target="_blank" rel="noopener">fino payment bank<span>&nbsp;</span></a>)<br>- WhatsApp Banking (Chat with us on<span>&nbsp;</span><a href="https://wa.me/8657008036" target="_blank" rel="noopener">8657008036<span>&nbsp;</span></a>)<br>- Monthly Account statements sent to your registered email ID</p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi faq-list_faqItemHidden__BUhla" aria-hidden="true"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-8" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-8" tabindex="-1"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">Can I add a nominee to my FinoPay Savings Account? How many nominees can I add?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-8" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-8" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p>Yes, you can add nominee at any point in time and at any given time you can only have a single nominee registered on your account.</p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi faq-list_faqItemHidden__BUhla" aria-hidden="true"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-9" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-9" tabindex="-1"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">How can I add a nominee to my FinoPay Savings Account?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-9" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-9" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p>You can add a nominee to your Savings Account in one of the following ways:<br>- At the time of opening your Account<br>- Our Mobile App</p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi faq-list_faqItemHidden__BUhla" aria-hidden="true"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-10" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-10" tabindex="-1"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">Can I have an FinoPay Savings Account in joint mode of operation?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-10" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-10" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p>No, account in joint mode is not allowed.</p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi faq-list_faqItemHidden__BUhla" aria-hidden="true"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-11" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-11" tabindex="-1"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">Which Debit Card will I get with my FinoPay Savings Account?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-11" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-11" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p>Free Personalised RuPay Platinum Debit Card loaded with exciting offers and benefits. Click here to know more about our Debit card offers<span>&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.fino.bank.in/cards" target="_blank" rel="dofollow noopener">Debit card</a></p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi faq-list_faqItemHidden__BUhla" aria-hidden="true"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-12" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-12" tabindex="-1"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">Is PAN card compulsory for opening Savings Account?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-12" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-12" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p>Yes, as per regulatory guidelines, a PAN card is mandatory to open savings account.</p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi faq-list_faqItemHidden__BUhla" aria-hidden="true"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-13" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-13" tabindex="-1"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">What are the benefits of upgrading the account?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-13" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-13" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p>There are multiple benefits of upgrading the account, some of them include exclusive offers and product offerings, no limits on transaction amount and more than we will add from time to time.</p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi faq-list_faqItemHidden__BUhla" aria-hidden="true"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-14" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-14" tabindex="-1"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">What is the validity of the FinoPay Savings Account?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-14" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-14" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p>In case you have opened a minimum KYC account (Just with Aadhaar OTP and PAN), you need to upgrade your account within a year or else the account would be closed automatically.</p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi faq-list_faqItemHidden__BUhla" aria-hidden="true"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-15" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-15" tabindex="-1"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">How can I upgrade my account?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-15" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-15" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p><a href="https://apps.apple.com/in/app/finopay/id6474030952?mt=8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Click here</a><span>&nbsp;</span>to upgrade your account instantly or login to our App and click on Upgrade account.<br>Through app - You can also visit our nearest merchant point and upgrade.</p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi faq-list_faqItemHidden__BUhla" aria-hidden="true"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-16" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-16" tabindex="-1"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">Can I open FinoPay Savings Account using a mobile number which is not linked to Aadhaar and OTP comes on the number used to open account?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-16" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-16" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p>No, to open FinoPay savings account, the number has to be linked to Aadhaar and your journey will be rejected after entering Aadhaar and OTP received on the mobile number which is not linked.</p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi faq-list_faqItemHidden__BUhla" aria-hidden="true"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-17" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-17" tabindex="-1"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">Is PAN card compulsory for opening saving account?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-17" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-17" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p>Yes. As per regulatory guidelines, a PAN card is mandatory to open a savings account.</p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi faq-list_faqItemHidden__BUhla" aria-hidden="true"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-18" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-18" tabindex="-1"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">Can I get my debit card on my communication address which is not my permanent address?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-18" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-18" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p>As per process, your debit card would be dispatched on your permanent address.</p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi faq-list_faqItemHidden__BUhla" aria-hidden="true"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-19" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-19" tabindex="-1"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">Why to add a nominee to my account?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-19" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-19" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p>Adding a nominee to your account is the smart thing to do. In the unfortunate event of an accident or death, the funds in your account will be transferred to your nominee quickly and easily. You don't have to add a nominee if you don't want to Simply select the I don't wish to add a nominee option while you open your FinoPay Account. You can always change your mind and nominate an individual later.</p></div></div></div></div></li><li class="faq-list_faqItem__SoSTi faq-list_faqItemHidden__BUhla" aria-hidden="true"><div class="faq-list_faqItemContent__ib8hE"><button type="button" id="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-20" class="faq-list_faqQuestion__mjg34" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-20" tabindex="-1"><span class="faq-list_questionText__fDikt">What is FATCA declaration and why i need to make one?</span><span aria-hidden="true"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"><circle cx="10.9507" cy="10.9507" r="10.9507" fill="#414099"></circle><path d="M5.29439 10.9499H16.608" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M10.9509 16.6059L10.9508 5.29236" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></span></button><div id="faq-panel-_R_mf9m_-20" role="region" aria-labelledby="faq-button-_R_mf9m_-20" class="faq-list_faqAnswerWrapper__x8qiB" style="height:0"><div><div class="rich-text_rich-text-container__qMehz rich-text_richTextContainer__szad6 faq-list_faqAnswer__M2o8_"><p>FATCA stands for the Foreign Account Tax Compliance Act. RBI has made FATCA declaration mandatory for all bank account holders in India. FATCA is a self-certification provided by the bank account holders about their tax residence for their compliace with FATCA</p></div></div></div></div></li></ol><button type="button" class="cursor-pointer inline-flex items-center justify-center font-semibold transition-all duration-200 active:scale-95 px-[16px] py-[7px] text-sm rounded-full bg-[var(--color-1)] text-white border-blue-600 hover:bg-[var(--color-1-hover)] focus:ring-blue-500" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="_R_mf9m_" aria-busy="false" aria-disabled="false">Show More</button></div></div></section></main></div><footer class="footer_footer__e_ilT" role="contentinfo"><div class="footer_footerContent__lKQpT"><div class="footer_footerLogo__E95DU footer_footerSection__k9yVC" aria-hidden="true"></div><nav aria-label="Footer navigation" class="footer_footerLinksContainer__qD7rN footer_footerSection__k9yVC footer_footerLinksContainerDesktop__XVICj"><section class="footer_footerLinksSection__QDJoq" aria-labelledby="_R_bm_-section-0-heading"><h3 id="_R_bm_-section-0-heading">REGULATORY </h3><ol class="footer_footerLinksList__KMccw" aria-labelledby="_R_bm_-section-0-heading"><