xt","dynamic_fields":[{"heading":"Hamari Kahani, Customer Jubani","testimonials":{"schema_id":"69660f19c500e638b87c300d","schema_slug":"testimonial-card","dynamic_fields":[{"testimonial":"My name is Nikhil Patel and I’m a resident of Ahmedabad, Gujarat and I took a ‘Family floater’ Insurance cover through Fino in the year 2018. During my family emergency, this policy was of great assistance to my mom’s treatment. My fund disbursal was super smooth and hassle-free. ","provider_name":"Nikhil Patel","provider_designation":"","provider_location":""},{"testimonial":"I am delighted to share my positive experience with Fino Payments Bank in Bastar, Chhattisgarh. Living in a smaller town, accessibility to banking services can sometimes be a challenge. However, I was pleasantly surprised by the bank's commitment to customer convenience. What stood out the most for me was the availability of bank Merchants even on Sundays. ","provider_name":"Rohit Yadav","provider_designation":"","provider_location":""},{"testimonial":"My name is Ashish Behera and I stay in Chaibasa, Jharkhand. I wish to share my positive experience with Fino Payments Bank. My younger brother stays away from the family for education and therefore, Fino is a reliable to send/receive money anytime anyday. ","provider_name":"Ashish Behra","provider_designation":"","provider_location":""},{"testimonial":"My name is Amit Patel and I’m a resident of Jaipur, Rajasthan and I’d like to share our great experience with Fino Payment bank.I am grateful to know my family’s life savings that are invested in this company are protected by a simple but effective safeguard with this bank. Definitely happy we chose Fino Payment Bank!!! ","provider_name":"Amit Patel","provider_designation":"","provider_location":""}]}}]},{"schema_id":"69660f19c500e638b87c306c","schema_slug":"faqs","dynamic_fields":[{"heading":"FAQ's","type":"Full Page","max_faq_count":8,"faqs":{"schema_id":"69660f19c500e638b87c2ff5","schema_slug":"faq","dynamic_fields":[{"question":"What is a FinoPay Savings Account?","answer":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFinoPay Digital Savings Account brings you great benefits and features to help you save and grow your money. The account comes with a free Personalised Platinum RuPay Debit card and no commitment to maintain any minimum monthly average balance, all at a nominal annual subscription fees.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"Who is eligible to open a FinoPay Savings Account?","answer":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFinoPay Savings Account can be opened only by an individual resident of India and age between 18 to 55 years.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"How can I open a FinoPay Savings Account?","answer":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eYou can open FinoPay Savings Account through the option available in the FinoPay App or our website, links are given below:\u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTo download the app:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.finopaymentbank.mobile\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003efino payment bank\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThrough website:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://digisa.fino.bank.in/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003efino bank\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"What documents do I need to open a FinoPay Savings Account?","answer":"\u003cp\u003eTo open an account you need the following documents:\u003cbr\u003e- Aadhar Card\u003cbr\u003e- PAN Card\u003cbr\u003e- Mobile number linked with Aadhar.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"What does the Zero Balance feature mean?","answer":"\u003cp\u003eZero balance means, no need to keep any minimum balance in the account and no extra charges for balance maintenance.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"Are there any charges for operating FinoPay Savings Account?","answer":"\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.fino.bank.in/files/fino/media/post_attachments/sites/default/files/2025-10/English%20%26%20hindi_Saving%20account_Schedule%20of%20Charges_25%20Sep-2025%20%28WebSite%29%20All.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"dofollow noopener\"\u003eClick here\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003eto view the Schedule of Charges associated to a FinoPay Savings Account.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"What are the different ways I can add money/transfer funds to my account?","answer":"\u003cp\u003eYou can add funds to your Savings Account by one of the following ways:\u003cbr\u003e- Via any other bank\u0026rsquo;s NetBanking/Mobile app. Simply add your FinoPay account details\u003cbr\u003e\u0026ndash; Account number and IFSC code\u003cbr\u003e- Depositing a cheque/cash at any of our branches or merchant point\u003cbr\u003e- Using any UPI app using your UPI ID\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"What are the modes through which I can access and keep a track on transactions in my FinoPay Savings Account?","answer":"\u003cp\u003eWe offer multiple methods to track your FinoPay Savings Account. Here are a few ways you can do it:\u003cbr\u003e- Mobile App (To download, click on the link\u003cspan\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.finopaymentbank.mobile\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003efino payment bank\u003cspan\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e)\u003cbr\u003e- WhatsApp Banking (Chat with us on\u003cspan\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://wa.me/8657008036\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003e8657008036\u003cspan\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e)\u003cbr\u003e- Monthly Account statements sent to your registered email ID\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"Can I add a nominee to my FinoPay Savings Account? How many nominees can I add?","answer":"\u003cp\u003eYes, you can add nominee at any point in time and at any given time you can only have a single nominee registered on your account.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"How can I add a nominee to my FinoPay Savings Account?","answer":"\u003cp\u003eYou can add a nominee to your Savings Account in one of the following ways:\u003cbr\u003e- At the time of opening your Account\u003cbr\u003e- Our Mobile App\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"Can I have an FinoPay Savings Account in joint mode of operation?","answer":"\u003cp\u003eNo, account in joint mode is not allowed.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"Which Debit Card will I get with my FinoPay Savings Account?","answer":"\u003cp\u003eFree Personalised RuPay Platinum Debit Card loaded with exciting offers and benefits. Click here to know more about our Debit card offers\u003cspan\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.fino.bank.in/cards\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"dofollow noopener\"\u003eDebit card\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"Is PAN card compulsory for opening Savings Account?","answer":"\u003cp\u003eYes, as per regulatory guidelines, a PAN card is mandatory to open savings account.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"What are the benefits of upgrading the account?","answer":"\u003cp\u003eThere are multiple benefits of upgrading the account, some of them include exclusive offers and product offerings, no limits on transaction amount and more than we will add from time to time.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"What is the validity of the FinoPay Savings Account?","answer":"\u003cp\u003eIn case you have opened a minimum KYC account (Just with Aadhaar OTP and PAN), you need to upgrade your account within a year or else the account would be closed automatically.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"How can I upgrade my account?","answer":"\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://apps.apple.com/in/app/finopay/id6474030952?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eClick here\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/span\u003eto upgrade your account instantly or login to our App and click on Upgrade account.\u003cbr\u003eThrough app - You can also visit our nearest merchant point and upgrade.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"Can I open FinoPay Savings Account using a mobile number which is not linked to Aadhaar and OTP comes on the number used to open account?","answer":"\u003cp\u003eNo, to open FinoPay savings account, the number has to be linked to Aadhaar and your journey will be rejected after entering Aadhaar and OTP received on the mobile number which is not linked.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"Is PAN card compulsory for opening saving account?","answer":"\u003cp\u003eYes. As per regulatory guidelines, a PAN card is mandatory to open a savings account.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"Can I get my debit card on my communication address which is not my permanent address?","answer":"\u003cp\u003eAs per process, your debit card would be dispatched on your permanent address.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"Why to add a nominee to my account?","answer":"\u003cp\u003eAdding a nominee to your account is the smart thing to do. In the unfortunate event of an accident or death, the funds in your account will be transferred to your nominee quickly and easily. You don't have to add a nominee if you don't want to Simply select the I don't wish to add a nominee option while you open your FinoPay Account. You can always change your mind and nominate an individual later.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"question":"What is FATCA declaration and why i need to make one?","answer":"\u003cp\u003eFATCA stands for the Foreign Account Tax Compliance Act. RBI has made FATCA declaration mandatory for all bank account holders in India. FATCA is a self-certification provided by the bank account holders about their tax residence for their compliace with FATCA\u003c/p\u003e"}]}}]}],"breadcrumb":""},"media_file_banner":{},"member":{"name":"Parth","slug":"parth","description":"","facebook":"","linkedin":"","instagram":"","twitter":"","avatar":null,"absolute_url":"https://www.fino.bank.in/author/parth"},"updated_by":{"name":"Shristi Singh","slug":"shristi-singh","description":"","facebook":"","linkedin":"","instagram":"","twitter":"","avatar":null,"absolute_url":"https://www.fino.bank.in/author/shristi-singh"},"content":"Post Content","content_json":[],"content_html":"","slug":"individual","url":"/home"},"renderLayout":true,"publisherFontFamily":"@font-face{font-family: 'Poppins'; font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; font-display: swap; src: url(https://fonts.gstatic.com/s/poppins/v24/pxiGyp8kv8JHgFVrJJLucHtA.woff2) format('woff2'); unicode-range: U+0000-00FF, U+0131, U+0152-0153, U+02BB-02BC, U+02C6, U+02DA, U+02DC, U+0304, U+0308, U+0329, U+2000-206F, U+20AC, U+2122, U+2191, U+2193, U+2212, U+2215, U+FEFF, U+FFFD}@font-face{font-family: 'Poppins'; font-style: italic; font-weight: 500; font-display: swap; src: url(https://fonts.gstatic.com/s/poppins/v24/pxiDyp8kv8JHgFVrJJLmg1hVF9eO.woff2) format('woff2'); unicode-range: U+0000-00FF, U+0131, U+0152-0153, U+02BB-02BC, U+02C6, U+02DA, U+02DC, U+0304, U+0308, U+0329, U+2000-206F, U+20AC, U+2122, U+2191, U+2193, U+2212, U+2215, U+FEFF, U+FFFD}@font-face{font-family: 'Poppins'; font-style: italic; font-weight: 600; font-display: swap; src: url(https://fonts.gstatic.com/s/poppins/v24/pxiDyp8kv8JHgFVrJJLmr19VF9eO.woff2) format('woff2'); unicode-range: U+0000-00FF, U+0131, U+0152-0153, U+02BB-02BC, U+02C6, U+02DA, U+02DC, U+0304, U+0308, U+0329, U+2000-206F, U+20AC, U+2122, U+2191, U+2193, U+2212, U+2215, U+FEFF, U+FFFD}@font-face{font-family: 'Poppins'; font-style: italic; font-weight: 700; font-display: swap; src: url(https://fonts.gstatic.com/s/poppins/v24/pxiDyp8kv8JHgFVrJJLmy15VF9eO.woff2) format('woff2'); unicode-range: U+0000-00FF, U+0131, U+0152-0153, U+02BB-02BC, U+02C6, U+02DA, U+02DC, U+0304, U+0308, U+0329, U+2000-206F, U+20AC, U+2122, U+2191, U+2193, U+2212, U+2215, U+FEFF, U+FFFD}@font-face{font-family: 'Poppins'; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; font-display: swap; src: url(https://fonts.gstatic.com/s/poppins/v24/pxiEyp8kv8JHgFVrJJfecg.woff2) format('woff2'); unicode-ra